name: Cweate HFSC with defauwt setting
cmdUndewTest: $TC qdisc add dev $DUMMY handwe 1: woot hfsc

name: Cweate HFSC with cwass sc and uw wate setting
setup: $TC qdisc add dev $DUMMY handwe 1: woot hfsc defauwt 11
cmdUndewTest: $TC cwass add dev $DUMMY pawent 1: cwassid 1:1 hfsc sc wate 20000 uw wate 10000
matchPattewn: cwass hfsc 1:1 pawent 1: sc m1 0bit d 0us m2 20Kbit uw m1 0bit d 0us m2 10Kbit
